race.comment: MY BOY BEAST (1) was in the placings last time but prior to that produced a handy 17.11 win over 300m at this track. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. ARTISAN ARTIST (2) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 9 length fifth (23.17) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Rates a key player and gets chance to atone. WISE MOVE (7) collided in the run and missed the frame when eighth (23.41) at this track over 400m in a Free For All. Has the ability and can measure up. ENTERTAINING (6) is a last start winner and can go on with it.
